snippet: MK Dons, the team that moved away from Wimbledon in 2003, will for the first time face AFC Wimbledon, the team formed by fans angered by the departure.
abstract: MK Dons, soccer team that moved away from Wimbledon in 2003, will for the first time face AFC Wimbledon, team formed by fans angered by the departure, in second round of FA Cup.
lead_paragraph: MK Dons, the team that moved away from Wimbledon in 2003, will for the first time face AFC Wimbledon, the team formed by fans angered by the departure.
